To set environment, edit ahir_bashrc 
as indicated in the file and source it.

You must have llvm-2.8 and clang-2.8 
installed in order to use the tools.

Please read the LICENSE; any use of
the tools in this distribution implies
that you have accepted the terms 
outlined in LICENSE.

Before starting, you may want to read
the documents in  docs/pdf/*, and then
move on to the examples in examples/*.
	
